{"tid":162459,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)時凶感應 絕世天劫 明日之後","createTime":"2017-03-19T10:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T17:08:59.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c395f88ebfec42065adf8a938389d68f60842048","tid":162459,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:10:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqjACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=c2abb1de\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 按左下可轉CC台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqjACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=5494fc47\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/cf/DejaVuBigPoster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fcf%2FDejaVuBigPoster.jpg&h=4cc561db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/fc/Armageddon-poster06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ffc%2FArmageddon-poster06.jpg&h=891e86ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/58/The_Day_After_Tomorrow_movie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F58%2FThe_Day_After_Tomorrow_movie.jpg&h=bc58c67a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事於美東紐奧良（紐奧良）取景，一眾美國海軍及家屬參加海上嘉年華，在渡輪出發後不久，船上的汽車炸彈於2006年二月十九日，懺悔星期二早上十時五十分發生爆炸，造成五百四十三人死亡。<br />\n美國菸酒槍炮及爆裂物管理局（ATF）人員道格（丹佐&middot;華盛頓飾）接手調查案件，在找尋案件證據後，證實這為一宗恐怖襲擊案，在翻查現場附近行車天橋的錄像片段後，發現事發時間有一騎機車的人正在橋中心停下觀望。其後調查人員於現場發現一具女屍，這名女子名為Claire，她僅有三成身體遭燒傷，右手手指遭剪斷，並曾遭淋汽油，顯示她為另一宗謀殺案死者，但被試圖掩蓋成爆炸案死者，而案中的汽車炸彈經調查後證實Claire正是其車主。道格遂前往Claire寓所調查，在屋中發現不少染血繃帶及紗布、一把手槍、在電冰箱發現&quot;U CAN SAVE HER&quot;（你可以救她）的字句，在翻查電話錄音期間赫然發現自己的留言。雖然道格有戴手套調查，但其後他的同事卻指道格在Claire家中留下不少指紋，案件便開始變得不尋常，很像道格早曾到過現場似的..<br />\n<br />\n2.亞特蘭提斯號太空梭在執行任務時，遭到流星雨擊毀，而從美國東岸南卡羅來納州到芬蘭都有遭到流星撞擊的災情傳出。美國國家航空暨太空總署隨後發現是一個德州一樣大的隕石的引力造成小行星帶軌道變動，使小行星帶上的星體向地球撞擊，而該隕石也預估在18天後將撞擊地球，造成地球上包括細菌在內所有的生物滅絕..<br />\n<br />\n3.在一片已經極度融化的南極冰川上，古氣候學家傑克&middot;霍爾與同事弗蘭克和傑森在冰川上考察時，親眼目睹整個拉森冰架全部斷裂。傑克隨後將有關全球暖化調查結果，在新德里舉行的聯合國研討會上作出報告，聲明兩極冰川融化已經阻斷了北大西洋洋流的暖洋流，而這種情況繼續持續下去將會在未來形成另一個冰河時期。但參加會議的各國元首對此感到荒謬，美國副總統雷蒙&middot;貝克甚至把傑克的理論當作笑話看待..<br />\n<br />\n6 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02690ee5bbeb3d8071c61f0a3ae670a75bf966f","tid":162459,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1397aed9012171d355e85d6a9f72f9a1d9d6fbdc","tid":162459,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ddbc0952659aca5d7b8c7537a2f49c9d7486667","tid":162459,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52108193ae79ad76f2a7a547c6419dabdc9d216d","tid":162459,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T12:47:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"256c272ec294fc2500c4df5b2e